                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Techie murder
                            
	Houston, June 24 (PTI): An African American youth has been convicted of murdering an Indian software professional in 2005. Howard Dale Bellamy, 24, who robbed and killed 28-year-old Akhil Chopra in a park, is bound to spend the rest of his life in prison.                                                                                                                                                                          
